        image: "/images/tech-scene.jpg",
    },
    {
        title: "Commercial Growth",
        description:
            "LA's thriving business district means constant demand for commercial electrical construction and upgrades.",
        icon: `<svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/></svg>`,
        image: "/images/commercial-growth.jpg",
    },
    {
        title: "Energy Efficiency Focus",
        description:
            "LA residents prioritize sustainable living, driving demand for EV charging, solar, and energy-efficient systems.",
